## Dogfood Requirement

Once `npm run dev` runs, create this track in the running app before closing the session:

**Track: "Build Tracks v0.1.0"** (category: Project)

Items in order:
1. Read Sparky's TRACKS_README.md and bootstrap scripts in PathFinder
2. Complete WAI foundation in WAI-State.json
3. Scaffold Next.js app (package.json, tsconfig, config files)
4. Implement storage layer (src/lib/storage.ts)
5. Build API routes (CRUD for tracks + items)
6. Build dashboard page
7. Build track detail page
8. Write README.md
9. Copy bootstrap scripts from PathFinder
10. Create this dogfood track (blocked_by: 7)
11. WAI closeout — session summary, git commit

Items 10 is blocked_by 7 (can't create it until the page works). This proves the dependency system works.

